<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٤ - <span class="c2">((النهاية)</span>) لابن الأثير.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠, ٧٢, ٣١٣, ٣٨٤, ٣٨٥, ٤٣١)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
